market volatility as a result of the effects of COVID-19, global inflation rates, potential downturns including recessions, and similar effects, or other market conditions, which may not be predictable in future periods;
•
our ability to grow in other geographic regions and to manage our continued overseas growth and the impact of interest rates, market conditions, political development, armed conflicts, and the COVID-19 pandemic on these regions and transactions;
